The Importance of Performance Testing
Performance testing assesses how an application behaves under varying workloads, from normal user activity to peak traffic conditions. By identifying potential bottlenecks, slow response times, and system failures early, businesses can prevent downtime, improve user experience, and ensure operational efficiency.

GT Infotechâ€™s Performance Testing Services Include:

Load Testing: Evaluate system behavior under typical user loads.

Stress Testing: Identify breaking points under extreme conditions.

Scalability Testing: Ensure your software scales efficiently as user demand grows.

Stability Testing: Verify consistent performance over prolonged periods.

Bottleneck Identification: Detect and resolve issues that impact responsiveness and reliability.

